The paper discusses a framework for integrating Edge, Fog, and Cloud infrastructure for IoT applications. This involves topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC), networking (cs.NI), security (cs.CR), software engineering (cs.SE), and distributed systems (cs.Distributed Systems). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.DC and cs.NI, followed by cs.CR, cs.SE, and cs.Distributed Systems.
